heif.boxes

Class CleanApertureBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • heif.boxes.Box
      • heif.boxes.CleanApertureBox

  • public class CleanApertureBox
extends Box
    Represents the clap (Clean Aperture Box). It defines the exact area of the image to be displayed, cropping any padding. Refer to ISO/IEC 14496-12:2015 documentation in Page 157 for more technical details.

      • logBoxInfo

        public void logBoxInfo()
        Description copied from class: Box
        Logs the box hierarchy and internal entry data at the debug level.

        It provides a visual representation of the box's HEIF/ISO-BMFF structure. It is intended for tree traversal and file inspection during development and degugging if required.
